  <brief_title>P3 Study of Umbilical Cord Blood Cells Expanded With MPCs for Transplantation in Patients With Hematologic Malignancies</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 1-Year, Multicenter, Randomized, Open-Label Controlled Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Cord Blood Cells Expanded With MPCs for Hematopoetic Recovery in Patients With Hematologic Malignancies After Myeloablative Treatment</official_title>
